data.description: This alluring one-story, 4-bed, 2-bath home is truly a refreshing find. Upon entering, you'll be entranced by its enchanting features and coveted layout. The foyer guides to the open and airy living area that effortlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living room. This set-up is perfect for hosting guests and enjoying everyday life with loved ones. High ceilings in the living room create an ambiance of grandeur and openness. The kitchen, spacious and stylish, features sleek dark cabinets and a convenient center island for culinary adventures. The expansive master suite impresses with dual walk-in closets and a roomy 4-piece ensuite. Every bedroom boasts huge closets for storage. Beyond the lovely interior, the property offers a vast backyard with the bonus of no rear neighbors, ensuring a private and tranquil outdoor retreat. This home harmoniously combines style, functionality, and value, making it a must-see for those seeking a comfortable and beautiful place to call their own.
